strings:
<voice_0x01000BE5><se_def>Angelo: ...Right, we're safe in here.
You can talk again now.
<voice_0x01000BE6><se_low>King Trode: Good! Tell us what's going on! What ordeal do you intend to put us through next, hm!?

<voice_0x01000BE7><se_def>Angelo: Like I said, I'm sorry about before.
If I hadn't lied about the ring, Marcello would have been onto me like a shot!

<voice_0x01000BE8><se_def>Angelo: And I haven't got anywhere else to go
if I'm chucked out of here.
But I came to get you out, didn't I?
<voice_0x01000BE9><se_def>Angelo: Come on! Don't be angry! Anyway, let me show you something you won't have seen before.

<voice_0x01000BEB><se_def>Angelo: There!
And that's real blood on those spikes, you know.
<voice_0x01000BEC><se_def>Angelo: If I were to throw you in there and shut the door, your whole body would be skewered.
<voice_0x01000BED><se_def>Angelo: I could make you hole-ier than thou without so much as getting my hands dirty. Not bad, eh?

<voice_0x01000BF1><se_low>King Trode: <Cap><hero>!
Can you hear me out there?
There's a secret passage in here!
